1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:07,840
A thousand years ago,

2
00:00:07,960 --> 00:00:09,680
the fiend Xieyun was born.

3
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:12,360
It was formed from the evil thoughts
of all living beings

4
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:13,600
across the Three Realms.

5
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:16,000
Its power was immense.

6
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,680
To prevent the Three Realms
from being plunged into chaos,

7
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,240
Immortal Venerable Jingwei

8
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:22,440
[Immortal Venerable Jingwei,
Supreme of the Immortal Clan]

9
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,640
forged Fushi Mirror to seal Xieyun away.

10
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:28,760
The Shadow Clan has repeatedly attacked
to seize Xieyun.

11
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,560
The Fushi Mirror was destroyed
by the Shadow Clan.

12
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,520
After escaping,

13
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:37,920
Xieyun unexpectedly entered the body

14
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:39,160
of a mortal youth, Mingling.

15
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:41,720
To save all beings in the Three Realms,

16
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:44,320
the Immortal Clan sought to
seal Mingling away.

17
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:46,960
But the High Immortal Bai Xiyin

18
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,480
refused to harm an innocent.

19
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,600
She decided to take Mingling
as her disciple

20
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:53,720
and grant him the immortal name Yaoyang.

21
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,200
[Records of the Celestial Venerables]

22
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,080
Sacrifice one to save the multitude.

23
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,560
But What has that one person done
to deserve this?

24
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,240
The multitude must be saved.

25
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:07,880
And so must

26
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:08,880
[Bai Xiyin,
High Immortal of the Immortal Clan]

27
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:09,880
that one.

28
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:28,920
It's the Shadow Clan.

29
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:29,880
Trouble!

30
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,720
Immortal Xiyin,

31
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,560
there's trouble!

32
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,040
Immortal Xiyin,

33
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,520
the Shadow Clan has launched
a surprise attack on us.

34
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,360
Our disciples have suffered
heavy casualties.

35
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,720
This time,

36
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,120
they're probably after Yaoyang again.

37
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,040
I understand.

38
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,320
You may go.

39
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,440
Understood.

40
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,200
[Yaoyang, Disciple of the Immortal Clan]
Without my permission,

41
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,560
you are not to leave Fuxian Abode.

42
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,320
I'm going with you to fight the enemy.

43
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,920
Your mind is not at peace right now.

44
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,520
The fiendish aura
can overwhelm your senses during battle,

45
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,400
and you could easily be controlled
by the fiend inside you.

46
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,000
The consequences would be disastrous.

47
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,240
Don't worry.

48
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,320
I can handle it.

49
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,320
Master!

50
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,800
Master!

51
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:12,360
Master, don't leave me!

52
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,200
Now the Shadow Clan

53
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,720
knows Xieyun is within Yang.

54
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,400
To seize Xieyun,

55
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,640
the Shadow Clan has repeatedly attacked
at any cost.

56
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,200
After repelling them this time,

57
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,360
I must find a complete cure

58
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,880
for Yang as soon as possible.

59
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,760
We can't keep going on like this.

60
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,120
I must defeat the Shadow Lord first.

61
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,250
[Shadow Lord,
Former Leader of the Shadow Clan]

62
00:03:02,250 --> 00:03:03,040
You are no match for me.

63
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:04,600
Where is Xieyun?

64
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,120
Hand over Xieyun!

65
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,320
Not a chance.

66
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,520
Yang!

67
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:49,840
Xiyin.

68
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,920
This is bad.

69
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,600
He's inhaled
the Shadow Clan's fiendish aura.

70
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,560
He's about to turn into a fiend.

71
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,520
No.

72
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,120
We absolutely can't let that happen!

73
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,000
Once he turns into a fiend,

74
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,920
the Three Realms will fall into chaos.

75
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:10,880
Immortal Venerable.

76
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,360
I can't let Yang continue like this.

77
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,880
Xiyin! Don't go!

78
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,720
Yang,

79
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,200
I will never let you turn into a fiend!

80
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,000
Master,

81
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,360
even you want to kill me?

82
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,400
Yang,

83
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,600
time is running out.

84
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,680
I have no other choice.

85
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:51,920
Master.

86
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:56,760
Xiyin!

87
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,360
Kill them all!

88
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,280
Attack!

89
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,160
Xiyin,

90
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,640
you would go this far for him...

91
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,440
Are you throwing your life away?

92
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:14,680
I never imagined

93
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,840
our master-disciple bond

94
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,520
would be so brief.

95
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,000
You're doing all this for him.

96
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,520
Is it worth it?

97
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,360
Yang,

98
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,600
I promised

99
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,600
to keep you safe.

100
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,520
[Chen Heng,
High Immortal of the Immortal Clan]

101
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:37,160
You always taught me
to see things through.

102
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,640
He is my disciple.

103
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,080
I can't

104
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:43,160
abandon him.

105
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,480
Heng, please, take him away now.

106
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:53,920
Master.

107
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,440
What's wrong with you?

108
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,600
Heng, hurry, take him away.

109
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,320
Master.

110
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,280
No.

111
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,600
I won't go!

112
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,600
Go now!

113
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,760
Master, please don't leave me.

114
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:05,960
Go!

115
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,000
Master, don't leave me!

116
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:14,920
Yang.

117
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,800
You must live on.

118
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,800
Today,

119
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:22,560
I will end this war for good.

120
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,520
♪This life feels like our first sight♪

121
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:29,390
♪For you, I drew the Three-Lives Blade♪

122
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:36,260
♪Carving eternity before your eyes♪

123
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:39,920
♪If saying goodbye aloud♪

124
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:43,760
♪Allows us to meet again♪

125
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:51,190
♪Please remember your promise♪

126
00:06:51,390 --> 00:07:01,340
♪Don't forget the vow you made♪

127
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:05,680
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 1]

128
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,040
Xiyin! Don't go!

129
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,040
Master,

130
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,680
please don't leave me.

131
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,600
Heng,

132
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,640
hurry, take him away.

133
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,160
Master, don't leave me!

134
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,880
Master.

135
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,080
Martial Uncle Chen Heng,

136
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:44,800
where's my master?

137
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,360
She's not coming back.

138
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,440
From now on,

139
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,320
you will focus on cultivation here.

140
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,600
Do not betray the care

141
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,800
your master had for you.

142
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,200
I'm going to find her.

143
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,400
Why is the immortal thread
between my master

144
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,320
and me gone?

145
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,280
What happened

146
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,720
to my master?

147
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,080
Can you please tell me?

148
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,520
She has perished.

149
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,960
Perished?

150
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,800
Impossible.

151
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,160
She promised

152
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,320
she would keep teaching me
different immortal arts.

153
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,200
I must find my master!

154
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,480
I've set up barriers all around.

155
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,320
Your power isn't enough
to break through.

156
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:36,320
Martial Uncle,

157
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,600
I'm begging you.

158
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,720
Let me go find her.

159
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:44,560
You're on your own now.

160
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,000
[Xinghong, High Immortal
of the Immortal Clan]

161
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,680
Immortal Venerable.

162
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,000
[Immortal Venerable Jingwei,
Supreme of the Immortal Clan]

163
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,840
The Shadow Army has been sealed away,

164
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,120
but remnants still lurk

165
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,520
within the immortal realm.

166
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,640
We must not let our guard down.

167
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:14,480
Understood.

168
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:17,160
We've already sent people
to search every immortal sect

169
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,600
for any remaining Shadow Clan members.

170
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,600
If we found them,

171
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,840
we'll eliminate them on sight.

172
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,200
Have you found Yaoyang?

173
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,560
Not yet.

174
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,320
High Immortal Xiyin sacrificed herself

175
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,080
to seal away the Shadow Army.

176
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,560
If the remnants obtain Xieyun,

177
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,040
they will surely return.

178
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,920
Whether Yaoyang is alive or dead,

179
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,280
he must be found.

180
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,400
Understood.

181
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,120
I have sealed away Xieyun within him.

182
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,000
He won't turn into a fiend again.

183
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,120
But the immortal sects

184
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:54,160
have always seen Yang as a fiend.

185
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,400
Heng,

186
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,480
if I am no longer here one day,

187
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,240
please

188
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,240
protect him for me.

189
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,920
Heng.

190
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,160
Heng.

191
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,200
Immortal Venerable.

192
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,240
You and your junior sister Xiyin

193
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,240
have been close since childhood.

194
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,800
Yaoyang is practically your disciple.

195
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,400
Where do you think

196
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,840
he might have gone?

197
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,280
Immortal Venerable,

198
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,960
he was stabbed in a vital spot by Xiyin.

199
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,640
I'm afraid he won't survive much longer.

200
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,480
Xieyun

201
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,760
will probably seek a new host.

202
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,080
Rest assured, Master.

203
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,320
I will spare no effort

204
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,280
to find the whereabouts of Xieyun.

205
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,600
Alright.

206
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:40,280
I'll leave this in your hands.

207
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,200
Understood.

208
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,680
Yang, here.

209
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,840
This is a birthday gift for you.

210
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,080
Master.

211
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,720
What am I to do

212
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:26,880
without you?

213
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,920
You wouldn't want me to become a fiend.

214
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,360
So this is the infamous little fiend.

215
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,480
I'm underwhelmed.

216
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,000
Just kill me if you're going to.

217
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,240
Stop wasting words.

218
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,400
You think I won't kill you?

219
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,800
You look so pitiful.

220
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,800
Beat me,

221
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,200
and I'll tell you

222
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,680
how to save her.

223
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,080
He's from the Shadow Clan.

224
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,960
He definitely doesn't mean well.

225
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,960
Fight back.

226
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,520
How will you win
if you don't fight back?

227
00:11:59,160 --> 00:11:59,960
But what if

228
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,720
he's telling the truth?

229
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,200
Don't you want to save your master?

230
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:04,760
Master.

231
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,160
Master.

232
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,160
I lost.

233
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,560
The Shadow Clan has a forbidden art

234
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,400
that can bring the dead back to life.

235
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,160
But...

236
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,120
But what?

237
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,640
But you might not be able to
pull it off.

238
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,600
Are you toying with me?

239
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,120
I can tell you how.

240
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,040
But whether it works

241
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,680
depends on you.

242
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,040
Master.

243
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,800
I promise I will save you.

244
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,360
This is the Fushi Mirror
that can save Master.

245
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,400
Yaoyang.

246
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,640
What are you doing?

247
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,440
Move!

248
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:41,800
Or I'll strike you down too.

249
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,680
[Forbidden Grounds
of the Immortal Realm]

250
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,320
Xieyun inside you

251
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,540
is suppressed
by a wisp of your master's soul.

252
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,120
Only the Fushi Mirror

253
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:12,640
can draw out Xieyun from within you.

254
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:14,920
[Gu Li, Young Lord of the Shadow Clan]
Then, with your master's

255
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:15,960
remaining soul fragments,

256
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,080
she can be reborn.

257
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,760
Fushi Mirror?

258
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,840
Wasn't it destroyed?

259
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,520
A damaged Fushi Mirror

260
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,960
just can't seal away Xieyun.

261
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,600
But it can still draw it out.

262
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,120
Master,

263
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,640
you gave up everything to save my life

264
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,600
and granted me this new beginning.

265
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,280
Though the Three Realms are vast,

266
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,720
you were the only one
who truly cared for me.

267
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,640
You never minded that I was a fiend.

268
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:44,440
Now

269
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,360
I'll also give up everything for you.

270
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,760
Even if I must oppose
the entire immortal realm,

271
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,400
even if I face eternal damnation,

272
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,280
I will bring you back to life.

273
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:09,780
♪I watch you descend
to the mortal world♪

274
00:15:10,620 --> 00:15:18,180
♪Slowly I let go of the thread I hold♪

275
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:25,060
♪If immortals can't linger for love♪

276
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:31,900
♪If mortals can't bind fate
for affection♪

277
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:35,300
♪Oh gods, please♪

278
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:39,260
♪Please show some mercy♪

279
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:48,620
♪Even if we must wait
another thousand years♪

280
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:51,760
[Bai Ruoxi, Embodiment of Xieyun]

281
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,420
Master.

282
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:08,980
Master.

283
